EN: We need to build a bridge to connect these two islands.

ZH: 他们构筑了一个围墙来保护农田。
EN: They constructed a wall to protect the farmland.

ZH: 这个小镇在几年前构筑了一座公园。
EN: This town built a park a few years ago.

ZH: 我们需要重新构筑这条道路，因为它有很多坑洞。
EN: We need to rebuild this road as it has many potholes.

